Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puella Magi Madoka Magica Episode 11 SHIT IS GONNA HIT THE FUCKING FAN!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.99,0:00:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time Traveler, Akemi Homura. {Time Reverser is awkward}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.42,0:00:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to rewrite the past, you have crossed multiple parallel dimensions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In pursuit of the ending that you wished for,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.07,0:00:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you have repeatedly traveled between dimensions for the past month, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.96,0:00:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your existence answered a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why Kaname Madoka possesses an incredible talent to be a Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now an acceptable hypothesis can be proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The potential to be a Magical Girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is determined by the amount of cause-and-effect carried.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.53,0:00:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A queen of a country, or a messiah will not be discussed,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.27,0:00:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but for Madoka, who grew up with an exceedingly normal life,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.62,0:00:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's hard to understand why such a huge cause-and-effect line is concentrated within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.30,0:00:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.49,0:00:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.38,0:00:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that Madoka became a powerful Magical Girl because of your constant repeating of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cause is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.13,0:01:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Specifically, it can be said to be a side effect of your magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.12,0:01:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is only one reason why you reverse time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.05,0:01:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the safety of Kaname Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.30,0:01:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the same goal and reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.00,0:01:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the course of going back in time countless times,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you could have probably twisted countless parallel worlds into a spiral.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kaname Madoka as the central axis.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.49,0:01:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's true,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.53,0:01:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the cause-and-effect lines of the impossibility of returning parallel worlds to equilibrium
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are all tied to Madoka, the axis of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So her unprecedented magical power index is immense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.01,0:01:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The time that you repeat
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.01,0:01:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,cycles all the cause-and-effect lines repeatedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And all of them are tied with Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.86,0:01:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything has led up to the current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.51,0:01:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work, Homura.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.32,0:01:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You made Madoka into the strongest Magical Girl there ever was.
