Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Missing since the 12th.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mitakihara Middle School 2nd Year, Miki Sayaka-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.01,0:03:46.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her body was found in a hotel in the city today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.69,0:03:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because the body's location did not show any signs of struggle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.85,0:03:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the police are investigating both the incident and the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.42,0:03:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the weather report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.44,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight, the Northwest wind will gradually get stronger, rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Madoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About Sayaka-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,do you really not know anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.82,0:04:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan and Kyoko-chan are both dead. {ANYONE READ ROSENCRANTZ AND GUILDENSTERN ARE DEAD?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not completely unexpected, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was foreshadowed a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to say that it doesn't matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.51,0:04:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though they died because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:52.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, do you feel any sympathy for farm animals?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.86,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the process they go through to become your food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of reasoning is too irrational.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.41,0:05:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you felt that the scene just now was cruel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then you didn't see it for what it really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.35,0:05:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were chosen to be food for humans,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.97,0:05:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and in exchange is protected from the competition of survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reproducing without natural selection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.23,0:05:23.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cows, pigs, or chickens.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.05,0:05:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the other wild animals,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.97,0:05:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,their reproductive success as a species is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.00,0:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we all want to live in an ideal environment of mutual survival?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.65,0:05:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that the logic is the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.02,0:05:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You might as well say that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,compared to the way humans treat farm animals, we've always been treating you very laxly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it, we only had business after confirming that you are intelligent organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.57,0:05:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll let you see some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,History tells that the Incubator and humans walked together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have prehistoric records of when we began to interfere with your civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:16.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Making contracts between countless maidens and Incubator.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.02,0:06:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Realizing their wishes, they then fall to despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.40,0:06:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting with a blessing, ending with a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.29,0:06:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, countless Magical Girls have repeated this endless cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.11,0:06:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This also brought many turning points in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.72,0:06:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People that bring society to a new stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.91,0:06:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Everyone believed in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.13,0:06:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clearly believing in you, yet only to be betrayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.11,0:06:48.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did not betray them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.17,0:06:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that it was their own wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what the wish is, even if it's something within rational bounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,can definitely create a twist of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.60,0:07:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And from that day on, it's only rational to proceed to the worst conclusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.41,0:07:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to call this kind of unpreventable conclusion a betrayal,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.45,0:07:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then the wish itself was a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, I wouldn't say it's foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of their sacrifice,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's true that the development of human history is pushed a little forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:30.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like that, in exchange for the the tears shed in the past, you have your lives now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:39.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you can correctly be aware of that fact, how can you treat these few people's fates differently?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been looking at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.52,0:07:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any sympathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:50.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you even tried to understand how painful it is for everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we could understand that,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then we wouldn't have come all the way to this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:07:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On our civilization's star,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.73,0:08:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,emotions are an extremely rare phenomenon and considered a mental illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:06.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we were surprised when we found you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.79,0:08:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A world where each individual has its own set of emotions, yet live in harmony.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have never even imagined such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.90,0:08:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you had never come to this planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be that you all would still be naked and living in caves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.70,0:08:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saying farewell to my own students in this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even knowing what exactly happened is even harder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.23,0:08:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a missing 3rd year, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every faculty member was stirred up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:46.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that nobody knows anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sayaka-chan seems to have had some problems with a friend involving love.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child was greatly impacted, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:09:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, that would end up becoming mere bittersweet memories,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.57,0:09:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it actually turned into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.38,0:09:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The police are planning to close the investigation
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.16,0:09:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by concluding the death was from weakness after running away from home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have any leads at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's Madoka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.31,0:09:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.61,0:09:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My instincts tell me that she should know something,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't tell if she's lying either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time that I couldn't see through her heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad, she's clearly my own daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shunko is actually saying pessimistic things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that she was acting pretty strange recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.52,0:09:44.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might be bearing some sort of burden on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.61,0:09:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how long I wait, she doesn't come and talk to me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had always felt that she relied on me quite a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.11,0:09:53.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kids that age...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will someday suddenly turn into adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although it's a shock for the parents...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.14,0:10:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can only believe in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.64,0:10:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now Madoka-chan needs time to properly sort out her feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to patiently wait it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.59,0:10:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not being able to do anything is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't always get what you want, Shunko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:24.88,(05:48 sign),,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1\3c&H1C2217&\pos(215,354)\c&H13190D&}Akemi Homura
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.28,0:10:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.98,0:10:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... Walpurgis Night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko-chan said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to eliminate a Witch that one person alone could not defeat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.49,0:10:49.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she must fight together along with Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were preparing here all this time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the whole city be in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's different from previous Witches.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one does not have the need to protect herself inside the barriers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She just has to materialize once,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and thousands of people will be sacrificed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.78,0:11:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, she must definitely be defeated!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.82,0:11:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko-chan is dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only Magical Girl that can still fight her is you, Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.98,0:11:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So—
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be enough by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without Sakura Kyoko,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can defeat Walpurgis Night by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.17,0:11:42.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyoko's help isn't something that I really need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just giving her some face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.02,0:11:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.26,0:11:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to believe in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.08,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to think that you're a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.25,0:12:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't feel like it will be so simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.52,0:12:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe that your words are true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.87,0:12:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I show you my true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.21,0:12:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I am...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.99,0:12:19.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and Madoka are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.41,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people living in different times!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a person from the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.22,0:12:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meeting Madoka over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also watching you die, over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.66,0:13:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I change destiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched for these answers, going back in time, over and over again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.64,0:13:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.58,0:13:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.78,0:13:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really ridiculous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.19,0:13:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sickening, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.99,0:13:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To you, I'm only...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.03,0:13:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a transfer student that you've barely known for a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:30.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you are....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.77,0:13:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more I go back,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the more skewed the time that you and I spend together become.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feelings are skewed too, and our conversations are gradually becoming impossible to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:46.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've probably been lost for so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.48,0:13:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.64,0:13:50.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.27,0:13:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was my final wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.60,0:14:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is already my final checkpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if you don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine if I can't make you understand anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.92,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I am still...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.86,0:14:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.92,0:14:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thunderclouds are breaking, gathering, and spinning with shocking power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's clearly a premonition of a supercell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Issue the disaster warnings immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.30,0:14:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.46,0:15:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, spending the night outside today?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Camping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.65,0:15:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today is a camp with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.51,0:15:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.97,0:16:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I must...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.22,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bring a conclusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, Madoka?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.82,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to the toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.13,0:18:22.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan said she can win by herself. Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I were to say no, would you believe me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, words are meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.59,0:18:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just watch how things end up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against the Walpurgis Night, how far can Akemi Homura go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.16,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she fight and risk everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.74,0:18:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because she is still pursuing hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.94,0:18:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she is forced to, she will also give up on this time axis, and continue fighting alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times, she refuses to quit;
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.68,0:18:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,therefore repeating this meaningless and endless cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.87,0:19:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To her, stopping is equivalent to giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she realizes that anything she does is meaningless...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:13.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When she realizes for certain that anything she does cannot change your fate,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.47,0:19:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akemi Homura will fall into despair, and become a Grief Seed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.57,0:19:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She understands that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, it is not up to her at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Regardless of if she can win or not, her only option is to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.98,0:19:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she believes there is hope, she can't be saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.43,0:19:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like all the past Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.24,0:19:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, you've seen it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.77,0:19:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, but!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.96,0:20:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.92,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am going to save a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to the firefighters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.63,0:20:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Outsiders should not interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.17,0:20:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life does not only belong to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.17,0:20:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing these kinds of reckless things will...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:24.02,Alt,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.50,0:20:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love Mama and Papa, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:36.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know how much you care about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.68,0:20:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I cannot throw myself away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.26,0:20:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is different!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because everyone is important, everyone must be protected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.33,0:20:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I have a place that I definitely must go to!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you tell me the reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.77,0:20:57.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring me along with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way, Mama should stay with Papa and Tatsuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.65,0:21:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let them worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.04,0:21:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mama, didn't you tell me that you raised me to be a good child?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.86,0:21:15.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not to tell lies, and not to do bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.77,0:21:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still trust me now, like you did before?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.02,0:21:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you still believe that what I'm doing is right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're definitely not doing something stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or being deceived by someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.34,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Mama.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.38,0:22:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it continues to advance...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.16,0:22:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to do something, to stop its advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.55,0:22:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.45,0:22:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why....?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.07,0:22:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I defeat it, no matter how many times I try?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.78,0:22:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everytime I go back in time, Madoka's burden will increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.79,0:22:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, the things I do are still...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.08,0:23:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Madoka, could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.82,0:23:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Homura-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.83,0:23:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone else tells me that having hope is a mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.91,0:24:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will reject that statement every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.60,0:24:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times I would have to.{ reject that statement}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.34,0:24:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My greatest friend.
